welcome_message_body: "Welcome to South Daytona! Get ready to experience the charm and beauty of our city, known for its stunning beaches and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that South Daytona has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Daytona Beach International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is used for domestic flights operated by Delta Air Lines.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is used for domestic flights operated by American Airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights and includes amenities such as restaurants, shops, and rental car services.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal caters to private and charter flights, offering a comfortable lounge and concierge services.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bunnell Flagler County Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Bunnell Flagler County Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: Terminal B at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves primarily international flights and is connected to the main terminal via a shuttle.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for up to two hours.
